{
  "title": "Peaceful Middle Eastern Lamb Tagine",
  "description": "A hearty and flavorful lamb stew infused with curry powder and aromatic spices, perfect for a lazy Sunday afternoon. This dish is slow-cooked to perfection in a rich and jammy sauce.",
  "cuisine": "Middle Eastern",
  "diet": [
